	Otavio R. Piske
	------
	Jan, 2013
	
Description

	Copies a file or directory
	
Element 

	Name: copy

Attributes

	from: source file or directory
	to: destination file or directory
	
Example

----------------------------------------
<copy from="${workdir}/${name}-${version}" to="${repository}" />
----------------------------------------
	